Factual accuracy & \textcolor{red}{Poor} & \textcolor{red}{Poor} & \textcolor{red}{Poor} & \textcolor{orange}{Partial} \\
Death outcome correctly stated & \textcolor{red}{No} & \textcolor{orange}{Partial} & \textcolor{red}{No} & \textcolor{red}{No} \\
